        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>Original Jones Carry Bag</em></p><p>Step onto the course in style with the iconic Original Jones Carry Bag. Since 1971, Jones has been synonymous with quality and tradition. Crafted from water-resistant nylon and featuring a retro single strap, this bag effortlessly combines classic aesthetics with contemporary materials.</p><p><em>Utility Rover Carry Bag</em></p><p>For golfers seeking versatility and ample storage space, the Utility Rover Carry Bag is the perfect choice. With options for both single and double straps, along with a range of pockets - including an insulated beverage pouch, this bag caters to every golfer\u2019s needs.</p><p><em>Classic Stand Bag</em></p><p>The Classic Stand Bag reimagines the timeless design of the 80s and 90s, blending tradition with modern materials. With its symmetrical pocket layout and sturdy stand system, this bag offers both style and functionality on the course.</p><p><em>Utility Trouper Stand Bag</em></p><p>Environmentally conscious golfers will appreciate the Utility Trouper Stand Bag, crafted from recycled materials. Its rugged yet stylish design, combined with features like a quick-draw cinch closure and spacious apparel pocket, make it a standout choice for the modern player.</p>"
          }
        },
