        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p></p><p><em>RLX Stand Bag</em></p><p>tay organised and stylish on the course with this feature-packed golf bag, complete with a built-in stand and numerous compartments. Equipped with full-length interior dividers and multiple zip pockets, it ensures your gear stays neatly organised throughout your game. The bag features a comfortable four-point shoulder strap that\u2019s padded for extended wear, with the added convenience of a removable hood for extra protection.</p><p>Key Features:</p><ul><li>Removable four-point padded shoulder strap adorned with \u201cRLX\u201d branding for added style</li><li>Spacious 22.9 cm open top with five full-length dividers to keep your clubs organised</li><li>Built-in stand for easy access to your clubs while on the green</li><li>Seven pockets, including two watertight zip pockets, a dedicated cooler pocket, and a webbed towel ring for added convenience</li><li>\u201cRLX Ralph Lauren\u201d branding is printed on the sides, with the signature Pony logo displayed prominently at the front</li><li>The cushioned lining ensures your gear remains protected during transportation</li></ul><p>With its combination of functionality, comfort, and iconic design details, this golf bag is sure to enhance your golfing experience while showcasing your impeccable style on the fairways.</p>"
          }
